{"title":"章氏“政治设计院”","authors":["俯拾"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":7,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"章氏“政治设计院”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俯拾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天下院子很多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"章氏要捞一个，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要的什么样子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吵架院——进口美货。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这玩艺儿好啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吵的资本家变肥鹅！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农人民吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“自由”卖血；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“平等”挨饿；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要想反对，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪打脑壳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妙呀！看实行了的蒋家哥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"院子一家人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收买、请客，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打架、抬出棺材来争夺！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"院子还多哩："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妓院、按摩院、疯人院……，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈的巴子“政治设计”真阔！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨煞我章氏“现在部里的权限太小”呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘿！一想起这些，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“非造反不可”！！！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎哟哟，章大哥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“人大”、“政协”顶不错，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宪法由它制，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民主计划经它做，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民生活提得多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有“政治设计”呀："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搬大山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清黄河……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还请你参加啰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"另搞一套是否妥？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呸！呸！呸！喽啰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真胡说！快把“人大”……什么的给我丢下字纸箩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要的是打倒他们的“设计院”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由我章氏当中坐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“政治设计”，不必啰嗦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照抄美、蒋的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现成的牛奶还不喝？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啐！别多心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"里面没毒药，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想想呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我随时可能发展为反革命”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搞这一套不正好么！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}